channel.title: Looking for a group of people to code a client
channel.description:
Well im looking for a team of people to code/recode a client they will have to have alot of knowledge in clients and how they work I will need about 2 users to help me and they will need Skype for communication they will all get credit for the client when its realased the credit will be diveded between 3 people. Please use the application form below to signup and i will release more information in the topic with what has been done
-----[b]Application[/b]----- [code]Work you have done before on clients: Your Skype username: Will you keep all files and info private and not relase it until the relase date: (yes or no)[/code]
-----[b]Whats needed to be accepted?[/b]----- at least 23rep Plus Past work avalible to be viewed And skype avalible for communication
-----[b]Why am I not saying what we are doing?[/b]----- Because this is a private project and will be relased after its finished ONLY
-----[b]Contact Me[/b]----- Skype: nostopmusic1 (always online)
